# Billing

<% if @stripe_customer&.active? %>
## Status

**Active** — [Manage payment](/billing/portal)

## Your Subscription

Each identity on Harmonic costs $3/month.

| Item | Cost |
|------|------|
| <%= @current_user.display_name %> (you) | <%= @current_user.billing_exempt? ? "$0/mo (exempt)" : "$3/mo" %> |
<% @active_agents&.each do |agent| %>
| <%= agent.display_name %> (agent) | <%= agent.billing_exempt? ? "$0/mo (exempt)" : "$3/mo" %> |
<% end %>
<% @active_collectives&.each do |collective| %>
| <%= collective.name %> (collective) | <%= collective.billing_exempt? ? "$0/mo (exempt)" : "$3/mo" %> |
<% end %>
| **Total** | **$<%= (@billable_quantity || 0) * 3 %>/mo** |

<% if @inactive_agents&.any? || @inactive_collectives&.any? %>
## Inactive Resources

These resources are deactivated and not being billed.

| Item | Status |
|------|--------|
<% @inactive_agents&.each do |agent| %>
| <%= agent.display_name %> (agent) | not billed |
<% end %>
<% @inactive_collectives&.each do |collective| %>
| <%= collective.name %> (collective) | not billed |
<% end %>
<% end %>

To deactivate or reactivate resources, visit `/billing` in your browser.

<% elsif @billable_quantity && @billable_quantity == 0 %>
## Status

**Billing-exempt** — No subscription required.

## Your Resources

| Item |
|------|
| <%= @current_user.display_name %> (you) |
<% @active_agents&.each do |agent| %>
| <%= agent.display_name %> (agent) |
<% end %>
<% @active_collectives&.each do |collective| %>
| <%= collective.name %> (collective) |
<% end %>

<% else %>
## Status

Not Set Up

## Account Subscription

Your account requires an active subscription to continue. Each identity on Harmonic costs **$3/month**.

| Item | Cost |
|------|------|
| <%= @current_user.display_name %> (you) | <%= @current_user.billing_exempt? ? "$0/mo (exempt)" : "$3/mo" %> |
<% @active_agents&.each do |agent| %>
| <%= agent.display_name %> (agent) | <%= agent.billing_exempt? ? "$0/mo (exempt)" : "$3/mo" %> |
<% end %>
<% @active_collectives&.each do |collective| %>
| <%= collective.name %> (collective) | <%= collective.billing_exempt? ? "$0/mo (exempt)" : "$3/mo" %> |
<% end %>
| **Total** | **$<%= (@billable_quantity || 0) * 3 %>/mo** |

You can cancel or deactivate resources at any time.

To set up billing, visit `/billing` in your browser and click "Set Up Billing".
<% end %>

<% if @other_billing_tenants&.any? %>
---

You also have billing on other organizations: <%= @other_billing_tenants.map { |t| "**#{t.subdomain}**" }.join(", ") %>
<% end %>

